<h2>Emergency Patient Information</h2>

<p><strong>Full Name:</strong> <%= @patient.name %></p>
<p><strong>Blood Type:</strong> <%= @patient.blood_type %></p>
<p><strong>Allergies:</strong> <%= @patient.allergies.presence || "None" %></p>
<p><strong>Chronic Conditions:</strong> <%= @patient.chronic_conditions.presence || "None" %></p>

